Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:07.93,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな未来も　ふたりで見たかった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:14.48,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな想いも　伝わる距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:21.20,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}君の旅立ち　覚悟してたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:27.37,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}背中押す言葉　声にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:34.13,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}最後につよく　抱きしめたあと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:39.67,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}ぬくもりと同じだけの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:47.60,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀しみが　僕の心つつんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:53.73,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}優しくなるための　サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:03:00.40,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕だけの幸せをくれたひと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.99,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつかまた会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:08.79,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}本当の君が見つかるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:14.50,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑顔忘れないで

Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:07.93,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論何種未來 都想一同見證
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:14.48,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}有你伴我身畔 思緒才能傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:21.20,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}早已有所準備 你會踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:27.37,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}幾欲衝口而出 終究未能表達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:34.13,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}直至分別之際 深深擁抱過後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:39.67,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}與溫暖同等份量的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:47.60,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀傷將我的心包覆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:53.73,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}為了變得溫柔 就此別過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:03:00.40,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}令我獨佔幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.99,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至再會之日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:08.79,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至覓得真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:14.50,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}莫要忘記笑顏

Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能請你閃開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在那裡很礙事耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果站在同一條件上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花肯定會選我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不死心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少說三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如去找七顆珠子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連腳都跺不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跺不了腳沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你碰不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算碰不到 我也是第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花所期望的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰不到 說不出 看不見耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話可能不該講
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是你害她病了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但店長沒法重新出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是你害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓出來 差不多也該讓給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也能下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君先去吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許你去2樓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不許你去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你阻止不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許趁虛而入哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等 聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 島尾君…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不看這邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會大聲喊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那抬起臉來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉色似乎好了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 又發燒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瘦骨嶙峋的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著我的一雙大手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時機選的… 是不是不太對？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者說太唐突了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢生做第二人也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君… 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有肉體 就流不出眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡都去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是隨波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了誰… 為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我一個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店裡… 我不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房子鬧怪音？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是做過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是… 六花和我的臥室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:08:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能還是去美穗那邊比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎把手機落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我出去 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺早晚真會殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣可能還比較公平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算抹殺掉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次店長面前會出現其他男人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每次都要礙事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到店長死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有打算成佛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早晚吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是趁早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是願意成佛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體… 能借我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 六花 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 地震呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好養病才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有搖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 店裡沒事 好好睡著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體怎麼能借人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的 所以身體借我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我怎麼可能答應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就詛咒你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你有點怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君 手機找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說店裡怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明搖的那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長 退燒以後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能教我和美穗怎麼進貨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店裡拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你不是說要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體借我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會還你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢生做第二人也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作不能不做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你消失掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在代替六花監視你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是有在幹活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的事 你考慮下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能借你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要睡著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是… 真正的地震吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算應付過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 今天有地震過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有地震嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望六花能早點好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次碰到店長病倒的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越健康的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體要垮掉的時候越沒有自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而讓人害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 幸虧明天店裡休息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在突然餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱倆難得一起來店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去坐坐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是日本酒好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和六花也常喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在便宜的居酒屋什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便吃個飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 六花沒有意中人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然說起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家父母經常給推薦相親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世道 當個花店的入贅女婿也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果對方條件好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把店關了也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是你弟弟的店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西需要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要有人從背後推一把
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺她沒什麼男人緣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為大姑姐 還算有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能是我多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在過於可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都被慣壞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長說 丈夫讓她把遺物扔掉快點離婚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他有點冷冷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他生過大病住過院 之後就達觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達觀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎經常在想 自己身後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那哪裡是達觀的結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美穗小姐和弟弟像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父母總是寵著弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好 因為他從小就是個病秧子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說起來我有留手機照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三人經常一起玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去花屋的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個打擊大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長可愛的掉渣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 眼角有點像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說來也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是幾年前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多六七年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美穗小姐的電話真長壽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有換機種啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是弟弟住院前拍的最後一張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒捨得刪 隨身帶到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然像這樣存下拍照時的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要刪除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勉強自己裝作無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻強迫自己忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難面對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也要建個墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先前美穗小姐說過不喜歡剪的花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也開始這樣想了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真湊巧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺剪花像幽靈一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來是吸收陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從根部吸收營養的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果只把草從頭上剪下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開土壤 只看漂亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這種好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也似乎不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好枯萎掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好新芽的肥料去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的手 能耕地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能種樹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能播種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能背起店長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今後能讓她露出那種表情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒不要緊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天出了好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能請你馬上昏過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體借我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長有訂報紙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}吶 葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}葉月君！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然不怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喂 不許無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報紙不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次休息日一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推銷報紙的大叔給的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者 叫上美穗三個人也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不擅長賭博…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是乾花 還是盆栽？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只有一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能一直笑著


Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:31.91,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}いつも夢のなかでは　あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:39.13,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}どうして　ねえ　消えないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:43.21,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}I gave you everything. You gave me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.88,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}きっと　いつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.80,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}You're everything, still my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:53.01,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}愛しているんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:22:05.44,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}真夏に降った雪のような　それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:15.75,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会わなければ　こんなに切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:23.42,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}胸を締め付けることもなかった　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:35.77,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会えなければ　強さも優しさも　知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:44.98,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}目を閉じれば　すぐそこに　あなたがいる

Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:31.91,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}在夢中 你總帶著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:39.13,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}為什麼 揮之不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:43.21,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我給了你全部 你給了我何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.88,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}我堅信 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.80,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}你是我的全部 仍是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:53.01,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我都深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:22:05.44,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}彷如夏日飛雪 那是如夢似幻的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:15.75,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}若沒有邂逅你 便不會如此五味雜陳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:23.42,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}不會心如刀絞 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:35.77,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}若沒有邂逅你 便不知何謂堅強與溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:44.98,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}合上眼簾 近在咫尺 有你相伴
